Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.40,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:13.80,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Why were my cheeks so flushed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:28.84,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Why was my heart beating so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:35.20,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,My face still feels hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:37.98,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I feel strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is really annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guys in class 4 are slacking on the culture festival preparations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're having a “beauty contest” and ranking all the first-year girls instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think those jerks should take a good look in the mirror first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should rank the boys by their looks, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which guys are at the top of your list?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really know the boys in the other classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about Miyauchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you went home with him the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you get so close to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just stayed late to finish some executive committee work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way you're defending yourself just makes me more suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It must be embarrassing for you.{lolwut}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone... Everyone's just joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Its fine. I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... Can you read this later?{I misread "later" as "letter" the first 5 times I read this. Maybe we should change it}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s kind of like a love letter.{kind of like?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we only talked for the first time just the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's from this guy named Asano in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to make it sound like I don't like you, Miyauchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can I say this right? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he doesn't look like a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he's nice, but he is pretty plain looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanoka, tell us what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's stop spying on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You say that, but I know you're curious, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably just playing a joke on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you run away? That was a good chance to talk to him!
Comment: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's always tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should walk around the festival with him.{orig: You're going to look around the festival with him, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try going out with him once, and decide if you want to go out with him for real later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, but what do you do when you “go out” with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you can do a whole bunch of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like walk home together, visit his house, or take a walk in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A park?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you get a boyfriend, you'll be able to grow out of your brother complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have a brother complex!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... Tomorrow is my school's culture festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome to come if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't look too happy.{Is something bothering you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, promise me you won't get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem like a bad person, but the letter is written so casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought he might just be playing a joke on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't go on a date with someone I've never talked to before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really know him very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he wants to spend time with you, to get to know you.{comma splice imabadperson}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Futaba-chan said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't show me letters like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if the letter was written casually, he might be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should show important letters like this to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to get your advice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said, if you don't think he's a bad guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,try going out with him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you get along well, then you can continue going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you got really mad the other day when Miyauchi-kun simply walked me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about that. I won't treat you like a little kid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my own problem. I should make my own decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:20.99,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:52.39,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,This really has nothing to do with you, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't really think about seeing anyone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't take it so seriously. I was just hoping we could have a fun time together today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there someone else you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm actually really busy with my class's haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I've made you feel uncomfortable. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:45.10,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who needs to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:53.10,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why am I crying?{She says "That's weird" again—there's probably a better way to handle this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A picture of my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't come to the culture festival, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to see what your famous prince of a brother looks like at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:14:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. He's not good looking at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has a thick beard, and he even smells like an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he stinky? What does he smell like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He smells weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, put this in the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does it smell that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really stink, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:36.87,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,They're three runs down, and it's the bottom of the ninth with two outs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:39.26,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Runners are on first and third base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.73,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Yoshimura's up to bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:44.34,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Today, he's been up to bat four times and has hit two singles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:47.90,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,If he hits a home run now, the score will be tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:52.30,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,It's a big hit heading for right field! Foul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.73,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,A nice hit, but it didn't go straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:15:01.05,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Ueda is warming up in the bullpen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.92,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,but the coach, Ohmori, hasn't signaled yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.14,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,The second pitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:05.05,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,A hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.83,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,It's a line drive straight down the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:08.54,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,The runner on third is heading home! Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.18,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,The runner on first rounds third base and is heading for home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you help me with my homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Too much work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember any high school math.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop staring at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're distracting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For that one, just use the formula.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look over it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which part?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You messed up on the first calculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. I see. I do that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! The homework was due today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't finish in time! The teacher's coming soon!{totally not sexual at all}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:39.13,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,If Futaba-chan and the others saw Onii-chan, what would they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:48.47,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I guess he isn't really that cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leaving so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:17:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is your sister waiting for you at home with a nice dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't get agitated any more when I mention her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:18.90,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan always has a sullen look. I never know what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:29.56,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,He's mean and gets angry quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:34.86,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,but on the other hand, sometimes he's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:37.89,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,And it surprises me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd it go with the guy who wrote you that letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun at the culture festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:19:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If something is bothering you,\Nfeel free to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you worried because you didn't know how to handle a relationship with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I turned him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:21.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Were you worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were, admit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's 10 years too early for you to have a boyfriend.{cliché, much?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you'd stop treating me like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of adult would swing a grocery bag around like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you following me the whole way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why the hell would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just saw you on top of the hill over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How weird! You were spying on me and laughing at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't laughing at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine for you to swing the bag around. That's just like you, Nanoka.{probably should be shortened}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just called me Nanoka for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! You always call me, "you" so arrogantly!{clearly we should have a tl note about "omae" here}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to be arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You always surprise me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I like you, Onii-chan.{she didn't say DIE-SKI, so obviously she doesn't mean LOVEYDOVEY}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mean it like what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're weird, blushing like that! So weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you...
