Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think I have a brother complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just asked him for advice when I got a love letter from this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do I really have a brother complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sentenced to a brother complex!
